{"tid":659652,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ONEPIECE 海賊王 ワンピース904情報","createTime":"2018-05-10T04:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T15:31:19.000Z","uid":3020,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"1276529670b1dfa053c195ad10599bcdf80fd56c","tid":659652,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5692369454?see_lz=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5692369454%3Fsee_lz%3D1&d=3fHLkMD1HHb%2BTUAHXfv7rTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5de0f5e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5692369454?see_lz=1</a> .<br />\n<br />\n904 〝革命軍全軍隊長登場〟 <br />\n<br />\nバルディゴを失った革命軍は総本部&amp;幹部総会の会場をカマバッカ王国へ移す <br />\nジェルマは今回の件で世界政府から外れた <br />\n今回の世界会議では天竜人への宣戦布告するつもりの革命軍 <br />\n<br />\n一方グランドラインのルルシア王国の港町では黒ひげ傘下らしい桃ひげ海賊団が金品を奪っていた <br />\n天竜人への天上金まで奪われそうになるが <br />\n世界中に散らばってた4人の革命軍の軍隊長達が現れ <br />\n&ldquo;東軍&rdquo;軍隊長のベロ・ベティのコブコブの実の能力で力が込みあがり戦う意思を持った町の人達は革命軍の援護もあり撃退 <br />\n<br />\n桃ひげの懸賞金5千万と革命軍へのいつでも呼んでと連絡先を渡し去っていく <br />\n<br />\n世界会議まで後2日"},{"pid":"9e544e46892ce5fec5ab46b21f623fc61cb26f4a","tid":659652,"uid":69698,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"04&ldquo;革命軍隊出現了全軍首領&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n失去巴爾迪戈的革命軍將把總部和執行大會的地點轉移到王國Bakka王國<br />\n在這種情況下，耶馬不在世界政府之列<br />\n在這次世界大會上，革命軍隊打算向天龍人宣戰<br />\n<br />\n在接地線的港口城市桃花鬍子海盜Rurushia王國的可能下傘黑鬍子另一方面，他搶劫錢物<br />\nTenzin人很可能被搶走了天堂的錢<br />\n出現了分散在世界各地的四個革命軍隊的軍隊長官<br />\n&ldquo;Higashigun鎮&rdquo;的人強行貝羅貝蒂的部隊長Kobukobu的真正能力是有意向爭取上升寫也協助擊退的革命武裝力量<br />\n<br />\n桃鬍鬚獎金5萬，隨時致電革命軍呼喚雙手，消逝<br />\n<br />\n2天到世界大會"},{"pid":"6305bac84bdb9dc2bff754ebdccd3928dd1a71b9","tid":659652,"uid":3020,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9e544e46892ce5fec5ab46b21f623fc61cb26f4a","tid":659652,"uid":69698,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"04&ldquo;革命軍隊出現了全軍首領&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n失去巴爾迪戈的革命軍將把總部和執行大會的地點轉移到王國Bakka王國<br />\n在這種情況下，耶馬不在世界政府之列<br />\n在這次世界大會上，革命軍隊打算向天龍人宣戰<br />\n<br />\n在接地線的港口城市桃花鬍子海盜Rurushia王國的可能下傘黑鬍子另一方面，他搶劫錢物<br />\nTenzin人很可能被搶走了天堂的錢<br />\n出現了分散在世界各地的四個革命軍隊的軍隊長官<br />\n&ldquo;Higashigun鎮&rdquo;的人強行貝羅貝蒂的部隊長Kobukobu的真正能力是有意向爭取上升寫也協助擊退的革命武裝力量<br />\n<br />\n桃鬍鬚獎金5萬，隨時致電革命軍呼喚雙手，消逝<br />\n<br />\n2天到世界大會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"904 革命軍全軍隊長登場<br />\n失去了巴爾蒂格的革命軍把總本部和乾部開會的會場移到了卡瑪巴卡王國（人妖國）<br />\n傑爾馬因為這次事件被世界政府開除了<br />\n革命軍準備在這次世界會議對天龍人進行宣戰<br />\n另一邊，在偉大航路的露露西亞王國的港口城市，疑似黑鬍子團旗下的桃鬍子海賊團在搶金品<br />\n甚至連要給天龍人的天上金都給搶走了的樣子<br />\n在世界各地分散的4個革命軍軍隊長現身<br />\n&ldquo;東軍&rdquo;軍隊長貝洛&middot;貝提擁有kobukobu果實的能力（瘤？）<br />\n他說擁有戰鬥反抗意識的人們同時也將擁有革命軍的援護，擊退了桃鬍子<br />\n留下了桃鬍子的5000萬賞金和&ldquo;隨時聯絡革命軍的聯繫方式&rdquo;然後就離開了<br />\n距離世界會議還有2天"},{"pid":"ca8698ccccc21c7a9ddc2db511edc3a8ba524c6c","tid":659652,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"你上集都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9efc14669d411b929a135bfb5e3c34bffd85911","tid":659652,"uid":3765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"冇山治？"},{"pid":"e9e9c36f5029759659284da924ee2a1d4d2bd49f","tid":659652,"uid":5349,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"趕撚住去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n譯到鳩芝孖碌都擺上黎咁撚驚人搶po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcf8493ef1161de4518e340f33e1023c0eb169b","tid":659652,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e9e9c36f5029759659284da924ee2a1d4d2bd49f","tid":659652,"uid":5349,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"趕撚住去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n譯到鳩芝孖碌都擺上黎咁撚驚人搶po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"post邊有搶同唔搶，從來都唔屬於任何人<br />\n因為呢D芝麻綠豆低能野可以咁介懷，真係好想知佢現實係一個咩人"},{"pid":"570ae3df594d0039164d5414983c96b3c7b2105c","tid":659652,"uid":3020,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/135953_1f77c90e0878e4c156fd43cbc3fe4ed3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F135953_1f77c90e0878e4c156fd43cbc3fe4ed3.jpg&h=18338cb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b79cefa491ef65a90267237c7127355b6dcead3","tid":659652,"uid":133252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"世界會議應該都要講成年"},{"pid":"19cba06777af8e4793b29a444b71d8766dbad7bf","tid":659652,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:20:00.000Z","msg":"Revolutionary Army moved its headquarter to Kamabakka Kingdom after they lost Baltigo.<br />\nMany RA including Ivankov already gather at Kamabakka Kingdom.Dragon decides to declare war against Celestial Dragons in Reverie.<br />\nFamous 4 RA commanders appear in Lurucia Kingdom (mentioned in chapter 903) where Pinkbeard is attacking citizens. Pinkbeard is under the umbrella of Blackbeard and has 52 million bounty.<br />\nName of the commanders<br />\nMorley (West Army) Giant. He appears from under the ground. His okama speech style is scary...<br />\nBelo Betty (East army) She calls the citizens in the kingdom as &quot;trash&quot; since they don't have the courage to fight pirates.<br />\nLindbergh (South Army)<br />\nKarasu (North Army) Karasu means crow in Japanese. Seems like Karasu is the one who were talking with Sabo in Dressorosa.<br />\nBelo Betty encourages the citizens to fight pirates with her DF called Kobu Kobu no mi, meaning encourage-encourage.<br />\nAs a result, citizens with RA commanders win the fight. Belo says that they never discard the weak citizens who have the courage to fight.<br />\nShe tells citizens to receive the award from WG about Pinkbeard.She gives a contact paper about RA and tells them to feel free to call RA anytime.<br />\n2 days are left until Reverie starts.<br />\nNo break next week"},{"pid":"4e068e0ae4eb0c53e772743a8f332ae18b734d3c","tid":659652,"uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/144357_664a12f98e6402fb755f6a2cf5a35643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F144357_664a12f98e6402fb755f6a2cf5a35643.jpg&h=ae6d30de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2af5ca0e4f1b1f267f60c5b2d545755bfdd36545","tid":659652,"uid":151333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"似係好幾個隊長之前都登場過"},{"pid":"251cf6ff10ebf5adef9dce34b6364728f8c33e28","tid":659652,"uid":143597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"尾田真係好鍾意畫人妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71238c266918ab33b4d3f3d43f3a79aa34280f49","tid":659652,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:28:14.000Z","msg":"究竟兩日會寫幾多集"},{"pid":"9c247c0c0dbc39b1d9f6a8e8c0e6d16f2d0280d1","tid":659652,"uid":90767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71238c266918ab33b4d3f3d43f3a79aa34280f49","tid":659652,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:28:14.000Z","msg":"究竟兩日會寫幾多集"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:38:24.000Z","msg":"2020年應